OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FA BBC programme which aired a claim
OL,7,Fthat Gerry Adams sanctioned the
OL,8,Fkilling of a spy would "probably" not
OL,9,Fhave breached broadcasting regulations
OL,10,Fand was not "unfair or unjust", a
OL,11,Fmedia expert has told a court.
OL,13,FChris Banatvala, who drew up the UK's
OL,14,Fbroadcasting rules for Ofcom and was
OL,15,Fits founding director of standards,
OL,16,Fcompiled a report based on a programme
OL,17,Fwhich claimed that Mr Adams had
OL,18,Fsanctioned the murder of Denis
OL,19,FDonaldson.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@aO]rD@MOUrD@^O]
