OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FMr Banatvala, who is an independent
OL,7,Fand media consultant, said that in his
OL,8,Fconclusion it is his view that the
OL,9,Fprogramme would "probably" not have
OL,10,Fbeen found to breach Ofcom's
OL,11,Fbroadcasting rules, and was not unfair
OL,12,For unjust.
OL,14,FMr Adams has claimed that the BBC
OL,15,FSpotlight programme, as well as an
OL,16,Faccompanying online story, defamed him
OL,17,Fby alleging he sanctioned the killing
OL,18,Fof Mr Donaldson.
OL,20,FHe denies any involvement.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@ZO]
