OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in 2006,
OL,7,Fmonths after admitting he was a police
OL,8,Fand MI5 agent for 20 years.
OL,10,FIn 2009, the Real IRA claimed
OL,11,Fresponsibility for the killing, and
OL,12,Fthe Spotlight programme was broadcast
OL,13,Fin September 2016 while a garda
OL,14,Finvestigation into the matter was
OL,15,Fongoing.
