OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FIn the programme, an anonymous source
OL,7,Fidentified as "Martin", who says he
OL,8,Fwas an informant for Special Branch
OL,9,Fwithin the IRA, claimed that the
OL,10,Fshooting was sanctioned by the
OL,11,Fpolitical and military leadership of
OL,12,Fthe IRA and that Mr Adams "gives the
OL,13,Ffinal say".
OL,15,FThe BBC has said the claim was
OL,16,Fcorroborated by five other sources.
OL,18,FThe High Court in Dublin heard that he
OL,19,Fwas asked to assess and produce a
OL,20,Freport on the programme by solicitors
OL,21,Ffor the BBC.
