OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FHe said: "What I have written is, on
OL,7,Fbalance, given the significant public
OL,8,Finterest, what information is already
OL,9,Fin the public domain about Gerry
OL,10,FAdams, the fact that the BBC
OL,11,Freasonably believed its primary
OL,12,Fsource, "Martin", to be credible and
OL,13,Freliable, that the BBC had
OL,14,Fcorroborative evidence from other
OL,15,Fcredible and multiple sources.
