OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,F"It was couched in terms of
OL,7,Fallegations, there was an appropriate
OL,8,Fand timely opportunity to respond, the
OL,9,Fprogramme would probably not be found
OL,10,Fin breach and not be unfair or unjust
OL,11,Fto Mr Adams."
OL,13,FHe said that Ofcom is not a fact-
OL,14,Ffinding tribunal.
OL,16,F"It is not there to decide whether or
OL,17,Fnot this allegation is true. What it
OL,18,Fis there to decide was whether making
OL,19,Fthat claim was unfair to Mr Adams,
OL,20,Fgiven all the circumstances and the
OL,21,Fprogramme as broadcast," he added.
