OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FHe also said that the allegation was
OL,7,Fof high public interest.
OL,9,F"It's of high public interest because
OL,10,Fit concerns a then elected politician,
OL,11,Fan allegation of serious misconduct,
OL,12,Fof potentially sanctioning a murder at
OL,13,Fa time when the IRA had a ceasefire,
OL,14,Fwhere the political progress had moved
OL,15,Ftowards peace, and he was responsible,
OL,16,Fallegedly, for sanctioning the killing
OL,17,Fof an informant.
OL,19,F"You couldn't get a more serious
OL,20,Fallegation or something of greater
OL,21,Finterest to the public."
OL,26,@qD@AOU{D@AOU}D@XO]
