OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FIn his report, he stated that an
OL,7,Fallegation that an elected figure
OL,8,Fsanctioned the killing of an informant
OL,9,Fin the context of that political
OL,10,Fenvironment is of the highest public
OL,11,Finterest.
OL,13,FHe also said the more serious an
OL,14,Fallegation is, the better the
OL,15,Finvestigation should be.
OL,17,FMr Banatvala added: "I understand that
OL,18,Fpeople have made allegations that he
OL,19,F(Mr Adams) was on the IRA army
OL,20,Fcouncil, and he's always denied it.
