OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,F"I also understand that he has an
OL,7,Falleged paramilitary background, and
OL,8,Fhe sanctioned murders. I also know
OL,9,Fthat he's vehemently denied that `
OL,10,Fthat I've known for the last 10 or 20
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"That does not mean that you can make
OL,14,Fany allegation against any person.
OL,15,FYou've got to have the evidence,
OL,16,Fyou've got to have your sources, but
OL,17,Fthat is the background in which you
OL,18,Fhave to make that particular judgment
OL,19,Fon that particular issue.
