OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,F"I think the programme is quite clear
OL,7,Fthat it explains that the programme is
OL,8,Fbased on a number of sources, whether
OL,9,Fthat is security forces, police
OL,10,Fforces, etc.
OL,12,F"With regard to the allegation against
OL,13,FMr Adams, post transmission
OL,14,Fcorrespondence is clear that the BBC
OL,15,Fclaims to have multiple credible other
OL,16,Fsources. I think it would have been
OL,17,Fhelpful for the audience to have
OL,18,Funderstood that, it would have perhaps
OL,19,Fgiven greater veracity to the story.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
