OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,F"Having said that, I don't believe
OL,7,Fthat that within itself would cause
OL,8,Funfairness to Mr Adams.
OL,10,F"Ironically, you could argue that,
OL,11,Fsaying that there are more sources out
OL,12,Fthere that agree with that claim, you
OL,13,Fcould say that actually that does
OL,14,Fpotentially more damage to potential
OL,15,Funfairness to Mr Adams, because it
OL,16,Fonly reinforces the allegation. So it
OL,17,Fworks both ways."
