OL,3,CBBC's Gerry Adams claim 'probably not
OL,4,Crule breach', expert says
OL,6,FMr Banatvala said it was also
OL,7,Fimportant to assess whether or not the
OL,8,FBBC states as a matter of fact that Mr
OL,9,FAdams sanctioned the murder, or
OL,10,Fwhether it put it in the words of an
OL,11,Fallegation.
OL,13,F"Obviously, if they state it as fact,
OL,14,Fthat means that it needs an awful lot
OL,15,Fof particular evidence that you can
OL,16,Fprove it. If you state it as an
OL,17,Fallegation, something that you have
OL,18,Fheard, you think is credible, you
OL,19,Fthink it's in the public interest to
OL,20,Ftransmit, but you cannot guarantee
OL,21,Fthat it's true," he added.
OL,26,@uD@AOU}D@PO]
