OL,6,F"If you take that in the round and the
OL,7,Fprogramme, and the fact there are
OL,8,Fsources, I think it's very evident on
OL,9,Fthis particular point that it was
OL,10,Fcouched in the terms of allegation."
OL,12,FMr Banatvala also said that Mr Adams
OL,13,Fwas given an "appropriate and timely"
OL,14,Fopportunity to respond to the
OL,15,Fallegations.
