OL,6,FMr Hogan then asked Mr Banatvala if it
OL,7,Fwas unusual for a programme's editor
OL,8,Fnot to be involved in engagement with
OL,9,FOfcom when it was investigating a
OL,10,Fcomplaint.
OL,12,FThe barrister noted that Spotlight's
OL,13,Fthen editor Jeremy Adams was not
OL,14,Flisted as a witness in the High Court
OL,15,Fcase.
OL,17,FMr Banatvala replied: "I believe he's
OL,18,Fno longer at the BBC."
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
